Springfield Boulevard, east side, between 113th Drive and 114th Avenue, showing one of the Hendrickson farmhouses. In 1891 it was on the 43-acre farm of P. C. Hendrickson. For additional Hendrickson houses in the old village of Springfield see other views of Springfield Boulevard.
